    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    Enquiry
    Represents an enquiry submitted by a user regarding a specific BTO project.
    HDBManager
    Represents a Housing Development Board (HDB) Manager who oversees BTO projects.
    HDBOfficer
    Represents a Housing Development Board (HDB) Officer who can register for projects and perform administrative tasks such as booking flats and generating receipts.
    Main
    The main class for the BTO Management System.
    Project
    Represents a BTO (Build-To-Order) housing project managed by the Housing Development Board.
    Receipt
    Represents a receipt issued when an applicant successfully books a flat.
